thread.title: BRIEF-UAE's Commercial Bank International FY Profit Rises

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-UAE's Commercial Bank International FY Profit Rises

organizations.name: commercial bank international fy profit rises feb

text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - COMMERCIAL BANK INTERNATIONAL PSC :
* FY NET PROFIT 175 ‍​MILLION DIRHAMS VERSUS 125 ‍​MILLION DIRHAMS YEAR AGO
* FY NET INTEREST INCOME 556 MILLION DIRHAMS, UP 10 PERCENT YEAR-ON-YEAR
* AS AT END-DEC 2017, CAPITAL ADEQUACY RATIO STAND AT 14.8 PERCENT VERSUS 14.4 PERCENT YEAR AGO Source: ( bit.ly/2E1jzRq ) Further company coverage:
